WHAT THIS REPOSITORY IS
-----------------------
A machine-readable dataset compiled and corrected by the IRONBUILT player community so that a
list-building tool can identify units and compute army costs. It is a community record, contributed
to and checked by its users. Corrections arrive from players and are recorded, with attribution, in
contributions/CONTRIBUTIONS.md.

The IRONBUILT application ships with NO game data. A user chooses to add a dataset from this
repository on first run, in the same "bring your own data" model used by tools such as BattleScribe
and New Recruit.


